0.00.name: wordpress/big-cartel-wordpress-plugin
0.00.description:
Pulls info from your Big Cartel Account into Pages on your Wordpress site. The Plugin allows you to create a few of the Main Big Cartel pages easily.

This is a very early version and I encourage others to contribute with ideas and code! There are a number of Basic TODOs, so if you're interested, contact me http://sites.google.com/site/sooperinc. Also feel free to donate! http://sites.google.com/site/sooperinc/donate

Version: 0.010

DATE: 03-25-10
